==Exchange Server系列==

Exchange Server 2007的MCITP以測驗考生對Exchange Server的規劃，設計，部署與維護的能力，並且做為微軟唯一的訊息化基礎架構解決方案（Messaging-based infrastructure solution），微軟對Exchange Server 2007的MCITP要求較嚴格。

'''MCITP: Enterprise Messaging Administrator'''
*前置需求：MCTS: Microsoft Exchange Server 2007 Configuration (70-236)
*考試：
**Exam 70-237: PRO: Designing Messaging Solutions with Microsoft Exchange Server 2007 
**Exam 70-238: PRO: Deploying Messaging Solutions with Microsoft Exchange Server 2007

Exchange Server 2010的PRO考試由兩科整併為一科，因此Exchange Server 2010 MCITP的考試由三科減為兩科：

'''MCITP: Enterprise Messaging Administrator 2010'''
*前置需求：MCTS: Microsoft Exchange Server 2010 Configuration (70-662)
*考試：
**Exam 70-663: PRO: Designing and Deploying Messaging Solutions with Microsoft Exchange Server 2010

