此為微軟首次針對專案管理（Project Management）所推出的MCITP認證，以Microsoft Project 2007與Microsoft Project Server 2007產品為主幹，因此前置需求即為該二項產品的MCTS認證。

'''MCITP: Enterprise Project Management'''
*前置需求：
**MCTS: Microsoft Project 2007, Managing Projects (70-632)
**MCTS: Microsoft Project Server 2007, Managing Projects (70-633)
*考試：
**Exam 70-634: PRO: Microsoft Project Server 2007, Managing Projects and Programs

